Draw underneath instead of on top of any existing page content.
.PP
\f[B]cpdf \-text\-width <string>\f[R] [\-font <font>] [\-fontsize <n>]
.PP
Return the width of a string of text in a one of the standard 14 fonts.
Used for calculations of text position (e.g right\-alignment).
.TP
\f[B]\-font\f[R] <font>
Specify the font.
.TP
\f[B]\-fontsize\f[R] <n>
Specify the font size.
.PP
