\f[B]\-bez23\f[R] \(lqx2 y2 x3 y3\(rq
Add Bezier curve to path.
.TP
\f[B]\-bez13\f[R] \(lqx1 y1 x3 y3\(rq
Add Bezier curve to path.
.TP
\f[B]\-circle\f[R] \(lqx y r\(rq
Add circle to path.
